  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 10th level, when you hit a creature with your natural weapons while you are raging, the beast within you can curse your target with rabid fury. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw (DC equal to 8 + your Constitution modifier + your proficiency bonus) or suffer one of the following effects (your choice):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>The target must use its reaction to make a melee attack against another creature of your choice that you can see.</li>\n<li>The target takes 2d12 psychic damage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you use this feature, you can't do so again until you complete a short or long rest.</p>",
